owlR 0.1.0
  • Reference

owlr

Installation

You can install this package from GitHub with:

library(devtools)
install_github("meerapatelmd/owlr")

Example

library(owlr)
#> Loading required package: reticulate
#> 
#> Attaching package: 'owlr'
#> The following object is masked _by_ '.GlobalEnv':
#> 
#>     read_owl
test_owl <-
  read_owl(
    file.path(
      system.file(
        package = "owlr", "owl"),
      "test.owl")
  )
test_owl
